Main features:

1. Summarize the text, store it in the title.
2. Pull score of credibility of website from nonprofits, add it to extension. With ranking.
3. Measure of sentiment.
4. RELEVANT NEWS ARTICLES




Optional. If we have time(probably not)
3. Metadata of website.
2. Analyze sentiment. To get score of how neutral article is.
4. Use the News Aggregation API (works like a search engine for news, where you import the news).

Source for data: https://mediabiasfactcheck.com



